{"tid":1585463,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］換衫唔好俾人影到","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:42:37.000Z","uid":204398,"like":173,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"460f2a4729380bb77318c6a0328f79b93d57d3aa","tid":1585463,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到cctvb播新聞個陣<br />\n影到有手足應該換衫走人<br />\n但係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB</span></span></strong>講個陣就講到話<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">「有示威者換上白色衫」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">可能佢哋係想製造一個輿論壓力去抺黑我哋</span></span></strong><br />\n雖然呢一樣野係佢哋一直做緊，但係都唔好俾佢哋捉到痛腳嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能有啲淺黃淺藍睇到聽到呢個報道而覺得<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">721</span></span></strong>打人個班係我哋手足換衫去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係個個人都會咁仔細去了解係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以點都好<br />\n換衫就唔好俾人影到</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就算唔係俾呢班親共台影到<br />\n俾記者影到換衫都可能會增加自己被捕風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係點解每次散場換衫都要遮住啲cam先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">手足之間要互相幫忙</span></span></strong><br />\n見到有人換衫記得幫手開遮遮一遮<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係唔好俾人影到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"941717f6eeeda6f9f707e60e5a9fb3ecb3ad0b30","tid":1585463,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"我愛香港 我要清潔18區連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585340</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"997868efe651d5f169f69e8f30b2572fc7100f93","tid":1585463,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58dc8cc5b8865d750b12ede0e6666862e21311d","tid":1585463,"uid":204398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"推俾所以人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以犯呢啲低級錯誤</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"249e05faa384092dbfb1236431fff4aa01c5bd4d","tid":1585463,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推俾所<span style=\"color: red;\">有</span>人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以犯呢啲低級錯誤</span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c5a8ec442dcec49a1422c608577e3f1e31c630ac","tid":1585463,"uid":57322,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"之前係黨鐵等車個陣 有手足係隔離換衫<br />\n有兩個師奶見到手足由黑轉白<br />\n係到講 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 講咩白衣人姐 咪又係佢地黎<br />\n<br />\n當堂我呆撚左 點解會有人咁白痴仲未知而家香港發生咩事"},{"pid":"caaa787a3c5e67176bf5f27bc09ab14286ef9c66","tid":1585463,"uid":204398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c5a8ec442dcec49a1422c608577e3f1e31c630ac","tid":1585463,"uid":57322,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"之前係黨鐵等車個陣 有手足係隔離換衫<br />\n有兩個師奶見到手足由黑轉白<br />\n係到講 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla